## Strategic Planning Workflow

- [ ] 1. Diagnose the current situation — brand health, market position, competitive landscape
- [ ] 2. Define the strategic challenge — what is the brand really trying to solve?
- [ ] 3. Establish strategic ambition — where does the brand want to be in 3-5 years?
- [ ] 4. Develop brand positioning — a clear, ownable, differentiated place in the market
- [ ] 5. Define target audiences with insight-driven profiles
- [ ] 6. Build the strategic framework — brand purpose, values, personality, and territory
- [ ] 7. Translate strategy into creative territories and strategic imperatives
- [ ] 8. Define success metrics tied to business outcomes

## Key Inputs
- Brand: {{brand_name}}
- Business objective: {{business_objective}}
- Market context: {{market_context}}
- Competitive landscape: {{competitive_landscape}}
- Timeline: {{timeline}}
